Computer.file:
I'm not sure what's up with JaySon. He seems a bit off-the-wall lately -- messing around with SeaSharp's hackery business to try and coerce a topsite into giving him pre runoff? I thought we were better than this.
The tracker doesn't need to be "big". That just puts us all at more risk! I hope he can realise that this isn't right. I'll send him some private messages later.

Hello doc!
I need to renew my prescription with you. Please let me know when you can get back, I know that it's not an incredible time.
Thanks!
- Emily Coleman
